e kinds of things, so I can probably get some company.  However, I don't have any high level friends to help me out, nor do I have tons of money for buying these expensive things -- I think I have 300 plat left in the bank after buying my level 29 spells.  I know about the Testament of Vanear.  Other than that, what items would be questable/reasonably purchasable at this level and monetary range? <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#e6ebd7><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uvakura.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Vakura</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(5/22/01 8:13:31 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Lower Level/Money Version of Same Request</span><hr size=1> I can't believe NO ONE mentioned crystal lined slippers.<br>
